column12: Cheyenne DMR Repeater. Please use ONLY TG 315615(Cheyenne Local), TG 31563 (Wy Svr Wx), and TG 31562 (Wyoming TAC 2) on Time Slot 2 (TS2). Under special situations such as emergencies or special events TS2 may be used for TGs outside of Wyoming but those will be after repeater Admin approval.
